* License         : MIT
  Programming Lang: Javascript                      
  Description     : Static and runtime type assertion library with no dependencies

  Typanion provides strong type inference; if your validator functions pass,
  TypeScript will refine values accordingly.

  Despite being very small, Typanion supports error messages, coercions, and
  various utilities outside of pure JSON validation.

  Typanion uses a functional approach that lends itself very well to being
  optimized away by most bundlers.

  This pacakge is needed for packaging yarn2 for Debian

